Record Date:10/12/2021 11:34 AM
Electronically Recorded King County, WA
Retum to: Erik R. Olsen/ls
Hanis Irvine Prothero, PLLC
6703 S. 234* St ., Suite 300
Kent, WA 98032
DOCUMENT TITLE:
CLAIM OF LIEN
GRANTOR(S)
EASTMAN, DONALD W.
GRANTEE(S):
FAIRWOOD GREENS HOMEOWNER'S ASSOCIATION
ABBREVIATED LEGAL
LOT 219, FAIRWOOD PARK DIVISION NO. 8, ACCORDING TO THE
DESCRIPTION:
PLAT THEREOF RECORDED IN VOLUME 85 OF PLATS, PAGES 77
THROUGH 84, RECIORDS OF KING COUNTY, WASHINGTON.
TAX PARCEL NUMBER:
247337-2190
Grantee claims a lien for unpaid assessments, fines, late fees, interest charges and attorneys' fees and
costs in the amount of $668.70 through October 11, 2021, against the above-described real property.
together with such additional assessments, attorneys' fees, late charges, interest, violation fines, costs,
penalties and other charges as shall accrue against the Property from the date hereof. At time of payment
of the total amount then owing under the provisions and terms of this Lien, Owner or the party remitting
payment will also be required to pay in advance the fees and costs for the preparation and filing of a formal
Release of Lien.
Unofficial Copy
Dated this _/ 2_ day of October, 2021.
ERIK R. OLSEN, being swom, says: I am the attorney for the claimant above-named: I have read the
foregoing Notice of Claim of Lien, know the contents thereof, and believe the same to be true.
FAIRWOOD GREENS HOMEOWNER'S ASSOCIATION
By:
Erik R. Olsen, WSBA #42947
SUBSCRIBED AND SWORN TO before me this 1/2"d
LAURA SANABRIA
NOTARY
PUBLIC
TATE
SHINGTON
day of October, 2021.
Daca Vomarius
Laura Sanabria
Notary Public in and for the State of Washington
Residing at Renton, WA
My commission expires on January 07, 2024
